 determine, in our or their sole discretion, that you may have engaged in abuse, misuse, or gaming in connection with your airline discount benefits. Tickets are non-refundable unless otherwise indicated. Tickets are non-transferable; name changes are not permitted. Changes to tickets (if permitted) may incur an airline-imposed change fee, and/or any difference in fare. Exchanges may not be permitted. Cancellations of tickets (if permitted) may incur an airline-imposed cancellation fee.
